TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Output-Investment Ratio and Input-Output Analysis
AU  - Lange, Oskar
AB  - [The paper shows that the output-investment ratio as well as the income-investment ratio is determined by the technological conditions of increasing production. The relation between sectorial allocation and physical composition of investment is shown. The question of maximising the rate of increase of national product or of national income, respectively, is discussed subject to the condition that minimal consumption requirements be satisfied.]
